sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户
    participant SCS as spec-coding-scaffold
    participant FS as 文件系统
    participant REG as module-registry.md

    U->>SCS: --level submodule --path submodule/XPPollingSDK --name XPPollingSDK

    Note over SCS: Phase 1 参数校验
    SCS->>REG: 检查 id 是否已注册
    SCS->>FS: 检查 path 目录存在

    Note over SCS: Phase 2 目标目录探测
    SCS->>FS: 扫描源文件扩展名
    SCS-->>SCS: 推断语言组合 OC+C++
    SCS->>FS: 解析 podspec s.dependency
    SCS->>FS: 扫描 import 语句
    SCS-->>SCS: 检测 touches_vehicle_sdk

    Note over SCS: Phase 3 生成骨架 6个文件
    SCS->>FS: .claude/CLAUDE.md
    SCS->>FS: .claude/rules/.gitkeep
    SCS->>FS: .ai-knowledge/specs/constitution.md
    SCS->>FS: .ai-knowledge/modules/.gitkeep
    SCS->>FS: .ai-knowledge/pitfalls/.gitkeep
    SCS->>FS: .ai-knowledge/deps.yml

    Note over SCS: Phase 4 注册
    SCS->>REG: 在 scaffold 标记区 append YAML block

    Note over SCS: Phase 5 待精修清单
    SCS-->>U: constitution TODO / deps TODO / keywords 默认值
    SCS-->>U: 子仓需单独 commit
